Find the beauty in terror in this new Japanese psychological horror.
 
When Shimizu Hinako's secluded town of Ebisugaoka is consumed by a sudden fog, her once-familiar home becomes a haunting nightmare.

Jared Hess (‚ÄúNinety-Five Senses‚Äù, ‚ÄúNacho Libre: Tudo pela Crian√ßas‚Äù), indicado ao Oscar, dirigiu Um Filme Minecraft a partir de um roteiro de Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, Neil Widener & Gavin James, e Chris Galletta, com argumento de Allison Schroeder, Chris Bowman & Hubbel Palmer, baseado no videogame Minecraft.
